          "reviewBody": "Dhruv Global School is doing excellent in all fields especially given a lot of exposure to children. Academic program are very nicely planned and organised. Great efforts by all teachers, staff members and management. My child is naturing and groomed very well.  I wish a great success to Dhruv global school. Proud to be parents of dhruvian child Master Viraj Tiwari. Jr KG A\n\nThank you",
