          "reviewBody": "It was the very first year of my child in Dhruv Global School.I am Impressed with your curriculum and the teaching methods. Well planned worksheets for practice.Our child always gets ample opportunities to explore and progress in all aspects. I am very happy to see improvement in my child.I like to take this privilege to congratulate the management of the School and especially both the class teachers Gunjan Mam and Bhagyashree Mam for their endless efforts.Will highly recommend Dhruv Global School.",
